When you look into someone's eyes, you can
understand their true nature. That's
what the old man used to say to me over
and over again.

I still haven't embodied those words of
the old man. After all, everyone around
me either has eyes filled with flattery
and deceit, or they look at my
appearance with disgust and hostility.

Hmmm... Does this mean that they understand my
true nature? No, that can't be right...
What the old man wanted to say wasn't
something like that.

But, I... have finally embodied it. The old
man's words were right. I could tell
just by looking into their eyes.

On that day... I came to a certain
television station, half for a meeting
and half to check out the new announcer,
MIsaki-chan.

A woman wearing a motorcycle suit jumped
into my field of vision as I got off the
elevator. For a moment, I thought she
might be a suspicious person or a
dangerous woman.

I first looked at her face to confirm her
appearance, as usual. Then, the woman
also turned her face towards me, so our
gazes met.

As soon as I looked into her eyes, I
understood. Ah, she's a completely
different person from me. And she has
lived a proper life until now.

......It was shocking. I never thought there
would be someone like this... In the
dirty side of the entertainment
industry, where I have been completely
tainted, I honestly felt that way.
......And I immediately came to this thought.
I want to completely dirty \{\{\{

How exhilarating would it be to stain that
innocent face with filthy pleasure and
bring them down to the same stage as me?

If it were an ordinary guy, it would just
end with thoughts. Even if they could do
it, they would just write it down in a
dark fantasy and be satisfied, and that
would be the end.

However, I am different from those small fries.
I have status, fame, and a vast network
of connections. Yes... I possess the
absolute power to make fantasies come
true.

So I immediately took action. While
preparing, every time I thought of them,
my dick would be fully erect without
fail. My dick was definitely yearning
for them.

Ah, it was such a fun time. It felt like I
had returned to my middle school days
when all I could think about was sex,
even though lately I've been having sex
while yawning.

......However, that time was finally coming to an end.
Surely... the days of spending such
hopeful moments will never come again.
Thinking that way, I feel a little bit
of sadness, but...
